channel_info.description:
I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife. 

I believe my experiences provide a rare balance of wild freedom and committed love, equipping me with the insights to help you navigate the complexities of dating and relationships in today's world. Let me guide you to embrace your desires, improve your social prowess, and ultimately attract the partner who aligns with your highest aspirations.

You won’t find any fluffy, new-age, or cringy stuff here, just tested, proven and actionable advice that yields results.

Apply to join our exclusive Inner Confidence Community of ambitious men who are actively working together to achieve their goals faster   ► https://innerconfidence.com/community

You can email me at robbie@innerconfidence.com with any questions or comments.

transcription: {"text": "How important is money? Money? There's a misconception out there that you have to have money to date women. But a lot of the teachings I talk about is show you how you can be a really successful guy actually being a minimalist. Now, is money a contributing factor? Sure, it's very helpful to have money because it signals so many good traits. It shows that you're driven, you have motivation, you're successful. So most of the time, guys who are broke that have no money lack a lot of those traits and therefore women aren't attracted to them for that reason. Now also, just because you have money doesn't mean you're gonna be successful. There's a lot of really rich guys who are boring duds and they do terrible with women. So if you don't have money, best bet is to get some motivation, get some drive, show all those characteristics, have a dream, have something you're working on. Now, just because you might not have money if you're young, women can certainly kind of hitch their wagon on the idea that you're going to be successful in the future. If you show a lot of that drive and motivation, they'll be very excited to see what's to come and they can be very attracted to that.
